text:
Lufkin-JT DQBigGame FOX SPORTS 
FOX Sports Southwest reporter Neil Beasley and multi-media host Kaime Stroot travel across Texas each week on the FOX Sports Southwest High School Express to the “DQ Big Game of the Week.” Lufkin's game against John Tyler on Oct. 9 has been selected by the network as the game for that week. Posted: Thursday, October 1, 2015 4:26 pm Lufkin's Oct. 9 game vs. John Tyler chosen as 'DQ Big Game of the Week' FOX SPORTS The Lufkin News
